import { Box,Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
// import photo1 from '../../../Photos/photo1.webp'
import Rough from './Rough'

function Product() {
  return (
    <Box style={{'display':'flex','justifyContent':'center'}}>
        <Box>
        <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="p"
          >
           Apple Product
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="h5"
          >
           Apple Product
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Box>
            <Rough/>
        </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Product
